 capital markets company overview of lincoln financial advisors corporation snapshot people company overview lincoln financial advisors corporation operates as a brokerdealer and investment advisor in the united states the company offers estate planning services in the areas of property ownership distribution strategies and estate tax reduction techniques and retirement planning services including needs assessment retirement income modeling benefits analysis and asset allocation strategies it also provides investment planning services such as advice consulting and planning portfolio modeling analysis and design development of investment policy statement implementation of manager search and selection and ongoing monitoring due diligence and reporting in addition the company of lincoln financial advisors corporation operates as a brokerdealer and investment advisor in the united states the company offers estate planning services in the areas of property ownership distribution strategies and estate tax reduction techniques and retirement planning services including needs assessment retirement income modeling benefits analysis and asset allocation strategies it also provides investment planning services such as advice consulting and planning portfolio modeling analysis and design development of investment policy statement implementation of manager search and selection and ongoing monitoring due diligence and reporting in addition the company offers business succession planning strategies that include buysell agreements such as stock redemption and crosspurchase agreements the use of life insurance grantorretained annuity trusts and family limited partnerships further it offers various products and services that include life variable life disability and long term care insurance products fixed variable and group variable annuities brokerage accounts and services asset management programs mutual funds and alternative investments retirement plans and client disclosures the 