ansformative people in the industry” by investmentnews and has been voted by readers of wealth management as one of the “four most influential people in the financial services field” ric has appeared on three industry publication covers financial advisor april  the register december  and real assets adviser january  and is a recipient of ernst and young’s entrepreneur of the year award for washington dc  and the us chamber of commerce’s blue chip enterprise award  ric is a distinguished lecturer at rowan university resident expert for dr oz and former columnist for financial advisor inccom and aarp ric is also a  new york times bestselling author with more than  million copies collectively in print his nine books on personal finance have been translated into several languages and educated countless people worldwide the truth about money was recognized with an excellence in financial literacy education eifle book of the year award from the institute for financial literacy march  a gold medal axiom award march  an apex award june  and a book of the year designation by small press magazine  the lies about money was awarded the axiom personal finance book of the year march  and an eifle award october  the truth about retirement plans and iras is a  national bestseller ric rereleased his  bestseller rescue your money which has been fully revised and updated to reflect today’s economy his ninth book the truth about your future was published in march  the ric edelman show has been airing on the radio for more than  years and is heard throughout the country ric has been named among the top  talk shows hosts for four years by talkers magazine which named him the th most important radio talk show host in america in  ric’s television series and specials the truth about money airs on public television stations across the us and in asia ric publishes an awardwinning page monthly newsletter offers free online personal finance education at ricedelmancom and speaks frequently at industry conferences ric has been featured in scores of articles has interviewed on hundreds of radio stations and every major television network and has been quoted by a vast range of newspapers and magazines he has testified before congress three times has participated in an sec roundtable and was appointed by presidents bill clinton and george w bush as a delegate to all three national summits on retirement savings ric taught personal finance at georgetown university for nine years and has guest lectured at roger williams university george washington university and rowan university where he was the first to be awarded the title of distinguished lecturer he is also a state and aicpaapproved instructor for continuing professional education and is a finra arbitrator ric graduated cum laude from rowan university in  the university bestowed upon him an honorary doctorate in  in december  ric graduated from the executive program at singularity university ric is on the advisory board of rowan university’s college of communication  creative arts and in  was inducted into the rowan public relations student society hall of fame the university named both its planetarium  and fossil park  after ric and jean edelman in recognition of their financial support to the university in  ric was named to the honorable order of the kentucky colonels ric served for five years on the board of the united way of the national capital area including two years as chairman he serves on the southeast board of the boys  girls clubs of america is a member of the boys  girls clubs of greater washington foundation board served on the bgcgw metropolitan board of directors for seven years and serves on the bgcgw leadership council he is a policy board member of the american savings education council and is on the foundation board of directors for the wolf trap foundation for the performing arts where he serves on the executive committee and is chair of the audit committee ric formerly served on the boards of junior achievement of the national capital area and the washington national opera ric and jean are benefactors of the inova edelman center for nursing at inova health foundation and the inova center for advanced medical simulation they are also supporters of the northern virginia therapeutic riding program heroes the makeawish foundation the leukemia  lymphoma society and other charities ric and his wife jean founded edelman financial services to provide financial planning and investment management services to everyday people today the firm’s  advisors serve more than  individuals and families from  offices coasttocoast managing more than  billion in assets the firm also provides k plans and institutional investment management for businesses efs has won more than  financial business community and philanthropic awards in  efs was ranked the  top independent advisory firm in the nation by barron’s previously it was named by inc magazine as one of the fastest growing privately held financial planning firms in the country three years in a row ric and jean live in the suburbs of northern virginia ric edelman executive chairman of edelman financial services llc a registered investment advisor is an investment advisor representative who offers advisory services through efs and is a registered representative and registered principal of and offers securities through ef legacy securities llc an affiliated brokerdealer member finrasipc forbes rankings are the opinion of shook research and are based on advisor interviews client retention industry experience compliance record assets under management and revenue generated for the firm investment performance is not considered advisors do not pay to be in the ranking according to barrons the formula used to rank advisors has three major components assets managed revenue produced and quality of the advisors practice investment returns are not a component of the rankings because an advisors returns are dictated largely by each clients risk tolerance the qualityofpractice component includes an evaluation of each advisors regulatory record the rankings are based on the universe of applications submitted to barrons the selection process begins with a nomination and application provided to barrons principals of edelman financial services llc selfnominated the firm and submitted quantitative and qualitative information to barrons as requested barrons reviewed and considered this information which resulted in the rankings on aug  aug  aug   the riabiz listing of the  most influential figures in the registered investment advisor industry is in recognition of notable driven and influential executives who are advancing their firms and are considered to be influential in the ria business investor experiencereturns were not considered as part of this ranking presented by the international association of registered financial consultants iarfc candidates must hold a professional designation and must have disseminated their comments on financial topics by having them widely published in articles journals books etc they must have provided outstanding personal service or leadership in the financial services industry nominees must have participated in some aspect of financial education to the public or to other members of the profession investor experiencereturns were not considered research magazine cover story “advisor hall of fame” december  based on serving a minimum of  years in the industry having acquired substantial assets under management demonstrating superior client service and having earned recognition from peers and the broader community for how they reflect on their profession investor experiencereturns were not considered as part of this ranking investmentnews th anniversary issue june   wealthmanagement madnessmarch  in  the truth about money th edition received the book of the year award from the institute for financial literacy for excellence in financial literacy education each year th